Diagnosis. The middle field of the epigynum is diagnostic in having a sclerotized Vshaped anterior margin, as well as the shape of the spermathecae (
Figs. 29­30
) and the colour pattern of opisthosoma (
Fig. 31
).

Known distribution. Angola , Zaïre and Guinea­Bissau (
Benoit, 1968
).
